data.description: Charming Oasis Awaits New Owners! Don't miss out on this turnkey home. Upon entering, you're greeted with the cozy front living space that flows right in to the dining and kitchen area. Kitchen is open and features updated GRANITE COUNTERTOPS and new STAINLESS FARMHOUSE SINK (2022). Past the kitchen in the SPACIOUS 2nd living area you'll find an inviting FIREPLACE that draws you right in and access to the backyard. Beyond the living is your very own COVERED PRIVATE PATIO and enclosed BACKYARD that backs up to a PARK. UPDATED VINYL FLOORS (2020) in living spaces and halls, WOOD-LOOK TILE in kitchen area. The hall bath has been updated with a NEW JETTED TUB AND TILE (2023) and GRANITE COUNTERTOPS. Additional updates include NEW HVAC and DUCT work (2021), ROOF (2020+/-) Converted garage to be converted back to single car garage. This space is perfect for entertaining or to keep as your private oasis, welcome home!
